    "description": "🗝️<strong>这是一款探索以石造墙壁区分为一个一个房间的RPG</strong>🕯️<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601280/extras/22d04bdfead334b331b71f9b47983044.poster.avif?t=1723080007\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601280/extras/22d04bdfead334b331b71f9b47983044.webm?t=1723080007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601280/extras/22d04bdfead334b331b71f9b47983044.mp4?t=1723080007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>踏足地牢，一点一滴地逐渐扩大活动范围！游戏地图将随着您的探索进展而同步更新。<br>游戏中需要动脑筋解开地牢中的奇异机关，收集宝物，加强调査队。 <br>当然，多种不同类型的怪物和BOSS在迷宫里恭候您大驾光临。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📖故事</h2>玩家是负责收集知识和魔法的物品调査队的成员之一。<br><br>调査队来到一个荒岛，寻找炼金士在地下迷宫遗留下的作物种子。<br>此种子是能抵受多年来威胁人类社会土壤污染造成影响的特殊种子。<br>以城镇遗址为基地，玩家在调査队队长的引领下，<br>一次又一次地穿越辽阔迷宫，勇闯存放种子的最底层为目标。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🪓战斗</h2><strong>防御，或者回避</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601280/extras/c31cfb7540183ee22b6e7ab89d5814e6.poster.avif?t=1723080007\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601280/extras/c31cfb7540183ee22b6e7ab89d5814e6.webm?t=1723080007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601280/extras/c31cfb7540183ee22b6e7ab89d5814e6.mp4?t=1723080007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>敌人的下一个回合会有图标显示。玩家需要作出防御、闪避还是攻击？<br>在知悉敌人行动的情况下选择下一回合的行动。活用丰富的情报进行战略是战斗胜利的关键之一。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👥角色</h2><strong>拥有职业和机能成长树的角色构建</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601280/extras/d765aebd209a4a848aee59e1ef5c4ace.poster.avif?t=1723080007\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601280/extras/d765aebd209a4a848aee59e1ef5c4ace.webm?t=1723080007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601280/extras/d765aebd209a4a848aee59e1ef5c4ace.mp4?t=1723080007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>尝试一下1+1=10吧！<br>在大本营中，玩家可以雇用调查员带着您去探险。当中有骑士、游侠和萨满等伙伴类别自由选择。 根据自己的喜好设定队员的发色或外观等。调査队中最多可有三位队员，怎样进行培训，要带领谁一起闯进迷宫等等，这些各种战略部署都是成功的关键。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📚探索</h2><strong>收集遗物，利用各种机关</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601280/extras/5c63aed18e74301795d6ba0ac05908cd.poster.avif?t=1723080007\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601280/extras/5c63aed18e74301795d6ba0ac05908cd.webm?t=1723080007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1601280/extras/5c63aed18e74301795d6ba0ac05908cd.mp4?t=1723080007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在地牢中有可能碰见邻近住民啊！跟他们聊聊天打探情况吧！",
